                "abstract": "Two populations of a declining western North American freshwater turtle\u2014one coastal and one inland\u2014were exposed to elevated water salinities of 10 ppt and 15 ppt over 2 weeks. Turtles from the coastal estuarine population had reduced feeding and drinking and maintained lower plasma osmolality levels than did those from inland.",
